Morgenstern, A. &amp; Parisse, C., (2012). &lt;a href=&quot;http://journals.cambridge.org/action/displayJournal?jid=JFL&quot;&gt;The Paris Corpus&lt;/a&gt;. Journal of French Language Studies, Cambridge University Press (CUP), 22 (Special issue 1), pp.7-12.</quote>
